{"tid":320441,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[4D3N]     慢活芽莊 享受一個悠閒的短假期","createTime":"2017-07-13T13:55:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-16T04:38:04.000Z","uid":16376,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"45b34d3692f40bb3392f7e8e9eb7337992de608c","tid":320441,"uid":16376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T13:55:14.000Z","msg":"如果你想個假期係慢活，放鬆悠閒，芽莊都係一個好地方，眼見好少關於芽莊既文，籍此就寫篇遊記，記錄低呢個慢活既城市。大家有咩都可以問我，始終芽莊既資訊唔多(峴港都可以）。我答到就盡量管<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家可以睇下條片先 概括左呢個Trip既行程<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Cb9KTJuRYZw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DCb9KTJuRYZw&d=IKE5B3xalFjF69%2F32X2Wuf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=6734133e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Cb9KTJuRYZw</a>"},{"pid":"adddf686db7464012a174b28c23970c765a24a41","tid":320441,"uid":16376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T13:57:09.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">Visa簽證 - 落地簽</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我早一個星期係cheapvisa搞，填曬個人資料，佢就會sd confirm email俾你，記得對資料，然後佢好快就會sd visa letter俾你，呢個時候你只要印好張野同visa form加2張相就可以。<br />\n<br />\n去到機場交曬D野俾海關等叫名，可能個陣我星期日，得兩個海關搞visa，明明我係第二個人，但都等左成個鐘。 價錢為USD 25 (海關收）＋ 8(cheapvisa）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">Sim Card ／換錢</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n出左禁區<br />\nUSD 1 = 20200 VND左右 <br />\n<br />\n未出禁區會係 <br />\nUSD 1 ＝20000 VND<br />\n<br />\nSim Card就30蚊RMB左右，都係出左禁區，換錢個到買。記得Test完真係上到網先好走，因為我不幸地買完張卡用唔到，個陣又走左。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">的士</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n市區內的士好平，坐30min都係12萬左右。而機場來往市區就30-35萬，呢個係唔計標的，記得上車前講價。"},{"pid":"7b62dcc05326204fef6635cd53452f894ba805b2","tid":320441,"uid":16376,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T14:09:10.000Z","msg":"我坐HK Express 1455機，但delay左一個鐘先飛，去到芽莊當地時間5點，搞埋visa 6點先出機場，book左3晚Sheraton，搭的士機場去市區預30-45分鐘左右。記得記得講價！！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/NV11RoQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FNV11RoQ.jpg&h=71b60f18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n去到check in 完都7點，book左樓下自助餐，200幾一個人，有好多野食，生蠔，蝦等等等咩都有，算對得住個價。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/eV0Zgwf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FeV0Zgwf.jpg&h=0d70e24f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/PZ9WZTl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FPZ9WZTl.jpg&h=5933addd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"93f7e2fa9e67d4c12a6404e3f8aa4538e798fd9d","tid":320441,"uid":16376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T14:26:20.000Z","msg":"第二日的去珍珠島，顧名思義係一個島，所以一係坐吊車一係坐船（多人先會開）入去。<br />\n島上面咩都有得玩，水上活動，機動遊戲，動物園都有，夠玩一日。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/NyUeKnA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FNyUeKnA.jpg&h=b6f0e743&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Ol9GBYc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FOl9GBYc.jpg&h=7c69e799&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/QxSdDFD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FQxSdDFD.jpg&h=f531b92e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/1fmEH1R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F1fmEH1R.jpg&h=b92d5f5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/FU9eOtu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FFU9eOtu.jpg&h=b0b71fe0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/tGurQzY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FtGurQzY.jpg&h=c38cba81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/BAHpnSj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FBAHpnSj.jpg&h=5e7f5da6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3f10168c95f55c4d2ebb41afa880482cb7a4aadf","tid":320441,"uid":52819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T14:45:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7767d4ba56f303941753073f94b63c6097877e87","tid":320441,"uid":95345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T14:48:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fad18a055d5688959eea6bcebb4837891e316f3","tid":320441,"uid":16376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T15:15:25.000Z","msg":"以為無人睇  btw如果有問題都可以問"},{"pid":"2401ee3652ff064ea2128532f2bab688955e7450","tid":320441,"uid":101557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T15:23:02.000Z","msg":"幾正"},{"pid":"38ac18f57e735111457694ed5868e04be54bfa72","tid":320441,"uid":16376,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T15:50:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾正</blockquote><br />\n個城市雖然唔多野玩，但真係可以好慢活同埋陽光與海灘"},{"pid":"51cf54dff0052b62f650c7f94402d2c9d6190c6d","tid":320441,"uid":16376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T15:51:10.000Z","msg":"第三日就係酒店成日，朝早食自助早餐，再係泳池游下水訓下食下野，咁就一日。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/I3t4CDc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FI3t4CDc.jpg&h=d110029f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a19f65ef08d175f530951912ee0fbeade750b8b0","tid":320441,"uid":16376,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T15:51:22.000Z","msg":"最後第四日係離酒店10分鐘路程既Nha Trang Center入面超市買下野，就番機場了。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果俾我揀日本定芽莊作為下次既假期，真係好大挑戰，但有時日本要食既野太多，要買既野都太多，反而唔可以好好享受一個假期，但係芽莊，真係可以好慢活咁過日子，加上酒店野又唔貴，可以叫room service，呢種生活態度都值得一試。"},{"pid":"a494a231ca2ecda8b9889ddba7df2a97fbf59b7c","tid":320441,"uid":5777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T15:56:10.000Z","msg":"珍珠島唔伏咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n黎緊去南越 兩日芽莊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b355dbec0c69df26dc9fb775619a89af2855cd64","tid":320441,"uid":16376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T16:07:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>珍珠島唔伏咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n黎緊去南越 兩日芽莊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上面條片都見到 其實幾多野元<br />\n前題你要中意水上活動 因為都好多選擇 <br />\n入場費800,000 VND"},{"pid":"22b222d3cbc3d11032907c632e86fe63b3cc5377","tid":320441,"uid":101557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T18:12:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>幾正</blockquote><br />\n個城市雖然唔多野玩，但真係可以好慢活同埋陽光與海灘</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n去過河內玩完都覺得好悠閒好正"},{"pid":"32157bf58697c1a59c330cd26fbfb3bdd3242caf","tid":320441,"uid":16376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T00:57:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>幾正</blockquote><br />\n個城市雖然唔多野玩，但真係可以好慢活同埋陽光與海灘</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n去過河內玩完都覺得好悠閒好正</blockquote><br />\n河內未去過 玩既野係d咩"},{"pid":"9e0f9c262a3dcaa40237190c91b20a0c8b3fdea9","tid":320441,"uid":32009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T01:52:39.000Z","msg":"黎緊去，有冇咩推介一定要去睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbb204a5abb751280dbb12a5f28cd0210f8990a4","tid":320441,"uid":16376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T02:40:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>黎緊去，有冇咩推介一定要去睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" 