://sapatoursfromhanoi.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/Hanoi-&ndash;-Sapa-&ndash;-Halong-&ndash;-6-days-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsapatoursfromhanoi.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2014%2F12%2FHanoi-%E2%80%93-Sapa-%E2%80%93-Halong-%E2%80%93-6-days-1.jpg&h=c4eda72e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSapa行下山睇景"},{"pid":"17b38e3ba793370bca7c25e264414feb410ef600","tid":320441,"uid":16376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T11:07:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>幾正</blockquote><br />\n個城市雖然唔多野玩，但真係可以好慢活同埋陽光與海灘</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n去過河內玩完都覺得好悠閒好正</blockquote><br />\n河內未去過 玩既野係d咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都好多地方去<br />\nHa long bay可以坐船玩兩日一夜<br />\n<img src=\"http://sapatoursfromhanoi.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/Hanoi-&ndash;-Sapa-&ndash;-Halong-&ndash;-6-days-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsapatoursfromhanoi.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2014%2F12%2FHanoi-%E2%80%93-Sapa-%E2%80%93-Halong-%E2%80%93-6-days-1.jpg&h=c4eda72e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSapa行下山睇景</blockquote><br />\n巴打影得好靚"},{"pid":"e932dbb3408dfd1dee57fc6efa8ed7fd882b9488","tid":320441,"uid":66825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T11:08:19.000Z","msg":"過癮"},{"pid":"35a96da9f773c636d864211664e100a4870d0176","tid":320441,"uid":16376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T11:35:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>過癮</blockquote><br />\n係幾過癮  好多香港人去旅行都係去盡每分每秒 <br />\n但越南正正因為無咩特別野買 行    所以可以好慢活"}]}